g.text: ?: Chance of this happening, depending on instructions in text
Wizard version intro contains numerous errors.
The original intro does not specify starting with a shield.
However, text and choices in the game assumes that you have one.
Take the talisman for +3ST after the Cave Troll unless your stamina is near full.
Lose the wooden tube after diving in the water if you are unlucky.
Skip the grappling iron if you have lost the rope.
Lose the mirror obtained from the elf woman at the basket lift.
Intentionally fighting the Guard Dog to refill luck.
Use skill potion either just before the Pit Fiend or the Ninja.
